Package org.beanio.internal.parser

Class PropertyComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.beanio.internal.util.TreeNode<Component>
      • org.beanio.internal.parser.Component
        • org.beanio.internal.parser.PropertyComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Iterable<Component>, Property, Replicateable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Bean, CollectionBean
    public abstract class PropertyComponent
extends Component
implements Property
    Base class for Property implementations that hold other properties (e.g. a bean object or collection).

    A PropertyComponent may only hold Property children.

    Since:
    2.0
